question: How many unique authors have written science fiction novels?
query:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

SELECT DISTINCT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?author) AS ?count)
WHERE {
  ?novel a dbo:Novel .
  ?novel dbo:genre|dbpedia-owl:genre "Science Fiction" .
  ?novel dbo:author|dbpedia-owl:author ?author .
}

    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Beatles>,

    <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stones>,

}
ORDER BY DESC(COALESCE(?numberOfSongs, 0))

query:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?property ?value WHERE {
  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wikimedia_Foundation> dbo:founder | dbpedia-owl:executiveDirector* ?person .
  OPTIONAL { ?person dbo:birthDate | dbo:dateOfBirth | dbo:dateOfDeath ?birthdate ; dbo:deathDate ?deathdate } .
  BIND (COALESCE(?birthdate, "N/A") AS ?valueBirth) .
  BIND (COALESCE(?deathdate, "N/A") AS ?valueDeath) .
  OPTIONAL { ?person dbo:positionHeld | dbpedia-owl:positionHeld ?property ; rdfs:label ?value } .
  FILTER( !ISBLANK(?value) )
}
